<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Faturanız Oluşturuldu! 🧾</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #e67e22;
        }
        .invoice-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .invoice-table th, .invoice-table td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .invoice-table th {
            background-color: #e67e22;
            color: white;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e67e22;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://i.imgur.com/kGseOlZ.png" alt="Şirket Logosu" style="max-width: 200px;">
        <h1>Faturanız Oluşturuldu! 🧾</h1>
        <p>Merhaba, siparişinize ait fatura oluşturulmuştur. Detayları aşağıda bulabilirsiniz. 📄</p>
        <p><strong>Fatura Numarası:</strong> {{ invoice.InvoiceNumber }}</p>
        <table class="invoice-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ürün Adı</th>
                    <th>Adet</th>
                      <th>Beden</th>
                        <th>Renk</th>
                    <th>Birim Fiyat</th>
                    <th>Toplam</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for orderItem in invoice.OrderItems %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ orderItem.Name }}</td>
                        <td>{{ orderItem.Quantity }}</td>
                        <td>{{ orderItem.Size }}</td>
                        <td>{{ orderItem.Color }}</td>
                        <td>{{ orderItem.UnitPrice }} TL</td>
                        <td>{{ orderItem.TotalPrice }} TL</td>
                    </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <p><strong>Genel Toplam: {{ invoice.TotalPrice }} TL</strong></p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">Faturanızı Görüntüleyin 📄</a>
        <p>Teşekkür ederiz! 💖</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
